98 class npc_lady_sylvanas_windrunner : public CreatureScript
99 {
100 public:
101  npc_lady_sylvanas_windrunner() : CreatureScript("npc_lady_sylvanas_windrunner") { }
102 
103  bool OnQuestReward(Player* player, Creature* creature, const Quest* _Quest, uint32 /*slot*/) override
104  {
105  if (_Quest->GetQuestId() == QUEST_JOURNEY_TO_UNDERCITY)
106  creature->AI()->SetGUID(player->GetGUID(), GUID_EVENT_INVOKER);
107 
108  return true;
109  }
110 
111  struct npc_lady_sylvanas_windrunnerAI : public ScriptedAI
112  {
113  npc_lady_sylvanas_windrunnerAI(Creature* creature) : ScriptedAI(creature)
114  {
115  }
116 
117  void Reset() override
118  {
119  LamentEvent = false;
120  playerGUID.Clear();
121  _events.Reset();
122  }
123 
124  void EnterCombat(Unit* /*who*/) override
125  {
126  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_FADE, 30000);
127  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_SKELETON, 20000);
128  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_BLACK_ARROW, 15000);
129  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SHOOT, 8000);
130  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MULTI_SHOT, 10000);
131  }
132 
133  void SetGUID(ObjectGuid guid, int32 type) override
134  {
135  if (type == GUID_EVENT_INVOKER)
136  {
137  Talk(EMOTE_LAMENT);
138  DoPlayMusic(SOUND_CREDIT, true);
139  DoCast(me, SPELL_SYLVANAS_CAST, false);
140  playerGUID = guid;
141  LamentEvent = true;
142 
143  for (uint8 i = 0; i < 4; ++i)
144  me->SummonCreature(NPC_HIGHBORNE_LAMENTER, HighborneLoc[i][0], HighborneLoc[i][1], HIGHBORNE_LOC_Y, HighborneLoc[i][2], TEMPSUMMON_TIMED_DESPAWN, 160000);
145 
146  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LAMENT_OF_THE_HIGHBORN, 2000);
147  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUNSORROW_WHISPER, 10000);
148  }
149  }
150 
151  void JustSummoned(Creature* summoned) override
152  {
153  if (summoned->GetEntry() == NPC_HIGHBORNE_BUNNY)
154  {
155  summoned->SetDisableGravity(true);
156  float speed = summoned->GetDistance(summoned->GetPositionX(), summoned->GetPositionY(), me->GetPositionZ() + 15.0f) / (1000.0f * 0.001f);
157  summoned->MonsterMoveWithSpeed(summoned->GetPositionX(), summoned->GetPositionY(), me->GetPositionZ() + 15.0f, speed);
158  summoned->CastSpell(summoned, SPELL_RIBBON_OF_SOULS, false);
159  }
160  }
161 
162  void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
163  {
164  if (!UpdateVictim() && !LamentEvent)
165  return;
166 
167  _events.Update(diff);
168 
169  if (me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING))
170  return;
171 
172  while (uint32 eventId = _events.ExecuteEvent())
173  {
174  switch (eventId)
175  {
176  case EVENT_FADE:
177  DoCast(me, SPELL_FADE);
178  // add a blink to simulate a stealthed movement and reappearing elsewhere
179  DoCast(me, SPELL_FADE_BLINK);
180  // if the victim is out of melee range she cast multi shot
181  if (Unit* victim = me->GetVictim())
182  if (me->GetDistance(victim) > 10.0f)
183  DoCast(victim, SPELL_MULTI_SHOT);
184  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_FADE, urand(30000, 35000));
185  break;
186  case EVENT_SUMMON_SKELETON:
187  DoCast(me, SPELL_SUMMON_SKELETON);
188  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_SKELETON, urand(20000, 30000));
189  break;
190  case EVENT_BLACK_ARROW:
191  if (Unit* victim = me->GetVictim())
192  DoCast(victim, SPELL_BLACK_ARROW);
193  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_BLACK_ARROW, urand(15000, 20000));
194  break;
195  case EVENT_SHOOT:
196  if (Unit* victim = me->GetVictim())
197  DoCast(victim, SPELL_SHOT);
198  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SHOOT, urand(8000, 10000));
199  break;
200  case EVENT_MULTI_SHOT:
201  if (Unit* victim = me->GetVictim())
202  DoCast(victim, SPELL_MULTI_SHOT);
203  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MULTI_SHOT, urand(10000, 13000));
204  break;
205  case EVENT_LAMENT_OF_THE_HIGHBORN:
206  if (!me->HasAura(SPELL_SYLVANAS_CAST))
207  {
208  Talk(SAY_LAMENT_END);
209  Talk(EMOTE_LAMENT_END);
210  LamentEvent = false;
211  me->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_KNEEL);
212  Reset();
213  }
214  else
215  {
216  DoSummon(NPC_HIGHBORNE_BUNNY, me, 10.0f, 3000, TEMPSUMMON_TIMED_DESPAWN);
217  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LAMENT_OF_THE_HIGHBORN, 2000);
218  }
219  break;
220  case EVENT_SUNSORROW_WHISPER:
221  if (Creature* ambassador = me->FindNearestCreature(NPC_AMBASSADOR_SUNSORROW, 20.0f))
222  if (Player* player = ObjectAccessor::GetPlayer(*me, playerGUID))
223  ambassador->AI()->Talk(SAY_SUNSORROW_WHISPER, player);
224  break;
225  default:
226  break;
227  }
228  }
229 
230  DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
231  }
232 
233  private:
234  EventMap _events;
235  bool LamentEvent;
236  ObjectGuid playerGUID;
237  };
238 
239  CreatureAI* GetAI(Creature* creature) const override
240  {
241  return new npc_lady_sylvanas_windrunnerAI(creature);
242  }
243 };

259  struct npc_highborne_lamenterAI : public ScriptedAI
260  {
261  npc_highborne_lamenterAI(Creature* creature) : ScriptedAI(creature) { }
262 
263  uint32 EventMoveTimer;
264  uint32 EventCastTimer;
265  bool EventMove;
266  bool EventCast;
267 
268  void Reset() override
269  {
270  EventMoveTimer = 10000;
271  EventCastTimer = 17500;
272  EventMove = true;
273  EventCast = true;
274  }
275 
276  void EnterCombat(Unit* /*who*/) override { }
277 
278  void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
279  {
280  if (EventMove)
281  {
282  if (EventMoveTimer <= diff)
283  {
284  me->SetDisableGravity(true);
285  me->MonsterMoveWithSpeed(me->GetPositionX(), me->GetPositionY(), HIGHBORNE_LOC_Y_NEW, me->GetDistance(me->GetPositionX(), me->GetPositionY(), HIGHBORNE_LOC_Y_NEW) / (5000 * 0.001f));
286  me->SetPosition(me->GetPositionX(), me->GetPositionY(), HIGHBORNE_LOC_Y_NEW, me->GetOrientation());
287  EventMove = false;
288  }
289  else EventMoveTimer -= diff;
290  }
291  if (EventCast)
292  {
293  if (EventCastTimer <= diff)
294  {
295  DoCast(me, SPELL_HIGHBORNE_AURA);
296  EventCast = false;
297  }
298  else EventCastTimer -= diff;
299  }
300  }
301  };
302 };

313 #define GOSSIP_HPF1 "Gul'dan"
314 #define GOSSIP_HPF2 "Kel'Thuzad"
315 #define GOSSIP_HPF3 "Ner'zhul"
316 
317 class npc_parqual_fintallas : public CreatureScript
318 {
319 public:
320  npc_parqual_fintallas() : CreatureScript("npc_parqual_fintallas") { }
321 
322  bool OnGossipSelect(Player* player, Creature* creature, uint32 /*sender*/, uint32 action) override
323  {
324  ClearGossipMenuFor(player);
325  if (action == GOSSIP_ACTION_INFO_DEF + 1)
326  {
327  CloseGossipMenuFor(player);
328  creature->CastSpell(player, SPELL_MARK_OF_SHAME, false);
329  }
330  if (action == GOSSIP_ACTION_INFO_DEF + 2)
331  {
332  CloseGossipMenuFor(player);
333  player->AreaExploredOrEventHappens(6628);
334  }
335  return true;
336  }
337 
338  bool OnGossipHello(Player* player, Creature* creature) override
339  {
340  if (creature->IsQuestGiver())
341  player->PrepareQuestMenu(creature->GetGUID());
342 
343  if (player->GetQuestStatus(6628) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE && !player->HasAura(SPELL_MARK_OF_SHAME))
344  {
345  AddGossipItemFor(player, GOSSIP_ICON_CHAT, GOSSIP_HPF1, GOSSIP_SENDER_MAIN, GOSSIP_ACTION_INFO_DEF + 1);
346  AddGossipItemFor(player, GOSSIP_ICON_CHAT, GOSSIP_HPF2, GOSSIP_SENDER_MAIN, GOSSIP_ACTION_INFO_DEF + 1);
347  AddGossipItemFor(player, GOSSIP_ICON_CHAT, GOSSIP_HPF3, GOSSIP_SENDER_MAIN, GOSSIP_ACTION_INFO_DEF + 2);
348  SendGossipMenuFor(player, 5822, creature->GetGUID());
349  }
350  else
351  SendGossipMenuFor(player, 5821, creature->GetGUID());
352 
353  return true;
354  }
355 };
